                           --AMIGADOS GUIDE V2.6--
                                     IDE


   DESCRIPTION:
   IDE (Integrated Drive Electronics) is a Hard disk Interface which is
   fitted as standard to A600, A1200 and A4000 computer systems.
   

   NOTES:
   IDE Hard drives are available in 2 physical sizes: 2.5" and 3.5"
   inches.

   There are also various flavours of IDE available including:
   E-IDE (Enhanced IDE), E-IDE UDMA.






